# 📊 Financial Analysis Dashboard with Power BI

This project provides a detailed financial and sales analysis using Power BI dashboards 
and a corresponding PowerPoint presentation. It visualizes performance across regions, products, and segments to
support data-driven business decisions.

---

## 📁 Project Contents

- `Financial Sample.xlsx` – Sample dataset used for analysis  
- `FinanceSales_Analysis_Task4.pbix` – Interactive dashboard with KPIs and trends  
- `Finance-Analysis-Presentation.pptx` – Clean, modern presentation of insights   
- `README.md` – Project overview and usage instructions

---

## 🔍 Key Features

- **KPI Summary**: Total Sales, Profit, Units Sold, Profit Margins  
- **Sales Trends**: Monthly performance, year-over-year comparisons  
- **Regional Insights**: Profit and sales by Region/country  
- **Product & Segment Analysis**: Top-performing products and segments  
- **Forecasting & Recommendations**: Actionable business suggestions  
- **Presentation Ready**: PowerPoint slides for reporting and sharing

---

## 🧠 Insights Derived

- Germany and France are high-profit regions  
- Paseo and VTT are top-selling and most profitable products  
- Seasonal trends impact profitability, peaking in Q4  
- Midmarket segment offers best return on investment

---

